ntouchable streak\", \"from\": 348, \"to\": 370}, {\"ngram\": \"domination\", \"from\": 374, \"to\": 384}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1,500-meter freestyle\", \"from\": 388, \"to\": 413}, {\"ngram\": \"10.33 seconds\", \"from\": 426, \"to\": 439}, {\"ngram\": \"11.14 seconds\", \"from\": 500, \"to\": 513}, {\"ngram\": \"bronze medalist Isabel Gose\", \"from\": 519, \"to\": 546}, {\"ngram\": \"a time\", \"from\": 562, \"to\": 568}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In typical fashion, Ledecky quickly put daylight between herself and the competition and kept building on it throughout the 30-lap race.\", \"from\": 583, \"to\": 719, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"typical fashion\", \"from\": 586, \"to\": 601}, {\"ngram\": \"Ledecky\", \"from\": 603, \"to\": 610}, {\"ngram\": \"daylight\", \"from\": 623, \"to\": 631}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 652, \"to\": 667}, {\"ngram\": \"the 30-lap race\", \"from\": 703, \"to\": 718}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Between Ledecky\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s performance and the ambitious, two-event night for French hero L\\u00c3\\u00a9on Marchand, the packed house was roaring all night.\", \"from\": 720, \"to\": 858, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 791, \"end\": 797, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.8666919287968573, \"rank\": 0.09274740128407666, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 809, \"end\": 817, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\", \"score\": 0.9999999917918103, \"rank\": 6.366590849613572e-09, \"text\": \"Marchand\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ledecky\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s performance\", \"from\": 728, \"to\": 751}, {\"ngram\": \"the ambitio