rom\": 1828, \"to\": 1843}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The eight gold medals ties Ledecky with fellow American swimmer Jenny Thompson, but hers all came in relay events.\", \"from\": 1867, \"to\": 1981, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1914, \"end\": 1922, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9998734122002949, \"rank\": 0.00011777449975701159, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1931, \"end\": 1945, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Thompson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jenny Thompson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Thompson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Thompson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The eight gold medals\", \"from\": 1867, \"to\": 1888}, {\"ngram\": \"Ledecky\", \"from\": 1894, \"to\": 1901}, {\"ngram\": \"relay events\", \"from\": 1968, \"to\": 1980}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Seven of Ledecky\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s eight are individual golds, which ties her with Czechoslovakian gymnast Vera Caslavska for most by a female, and third most by either gender.\", \"from\": 1982, \"to\": 2144, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2075, \"end\": 2079, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vera_Duckworth\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3455678383892938e-25, \"text\": \"Vera\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vera_Duckworth\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vera_Duckworth\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ledecky\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 1991, \"to\": 2002}, {\"ngram\": \"individual golds\", \"from\": 2013, \"to\": 2029}, {\"ngram\": \"a female\", \"from\": 2102, \"to\": 2110}, {\"ngram\": \"either gender\", \"from\": 2130, \"to\": 2143}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In total medal terms, Ledecky now has 12 (e